keyFacts: The document is a travel voucher for an Epstein investigation-related witness interview trip.
The trip occurred from February 26 to February 29, 2020, in Beverly Hills, CA.
The voucher total expenses were $1,059.52, with an estimated trip cost of $1,621.65.
The voucher was approved on March 3, 2020, and was awaiting further approval.
The document indicates ongoing investigative activity in the Epstein case as of early 2020.
